song.title: Luminator
song.info: All the lovely music from the Australian demoparty "Flashback 2013". As always the songs has been recorded from real hardware: Commodore 64 SID 8580R5 Commodore 64 SID 6581R4AR No normalizing, EQ, Compressor or Phase corrections! Just straight from the C-64er to the computer. (D)2013 Dees Productions
